OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FHundreds of police officers have taken
OL,8,Fpart in a crackdown on crime in
OL,9,FLiverpool.
OL,11,FA convoy of vehicles left the
OL,12,FMerseyside Police headquarters on the
OL,13,Fmorning of Wednesday 4 March 2026 as
OL,14,Fpart of the operation targeting
OL,15,Fcriminals in Anfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
