OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FA total of 34 people have so far been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of a number of
OL,9,Foffences including possession with
OL,10,Fintent to supply Class A and B drugs,
OL,11,Fsexual offences and possession of
OL,12,Findecent images.
OL,14,FThe day of action is the second which
OL,15,Fhas taken place since Chief Constable
OL,16,FRob Carden took up his post, in
OL,17,FSeptember last year, with a promise to
OL,18,Ftake those involved in criminality
OL,19,F"off the streets".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FHe said: "The scale and impact of
OL,8,Ftoday's operation should leave
OL,9,Fcriminals in absolutely no doubt ` we
OL,10,Fare here, we are watching and, if you
OL,11,Fare involved in criminality, you can
OL,12,Fexpect a knock on your door."
OL,14,FFourteen search warrants were carried
OL,15,Fout on Wednesday morning.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FThroughout the day residents can
OL,8,Fexpect to see teams of officers carry
OL,9,Fout land and underwater searches,
OL,10,Froadside operations and the targeting
OL,11,Fof suspects wanted for offences
OL,12,Fincluding domestic abuse, fraud and
OL,13,Fdrug-related offending, a spokesman
OL,14,Ffor Merseyside Police said.
OL,16,FAbout 300 officers and staff will be
OL,17,Finvolved in the large-scale operation,
OL,18,Fwhich the force says will effectively
OL,19,Flock down the area to allow them to
OL,20,Ftarget criminals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FMr Carden added: "Today's activity
OL,8,Fshows our complete and utter contempt
OL,9,Ffor those involved in criminality,
OL,10,Fwhilst at the same time giving the
OL,11,Fcommunity the compassion,
OL,12,Funderstanding and support they deserve.
OL,14,F"Our message to criminals is clear `
OL,15,Fwe don't want them in our communities
OL,16,Fand we will be relentless in our
OL,17,Fpursuit of them.
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"The protection of the public is a
OL,8,Fvital part of today and we will be
OL,9,Fsupporting and safeguarding vulnerable
OL,10,Fvictims, alongside our partners
OL,11,Fincluding Liverpool City Council and
OL,12,Flocal charities and support services."
OL,14,FThe leader of Liverpool City Council,
OL,15,FLiam Robinson, said: "The action being
OL,16,Ftaken by Merseyside Police today is
OL,17,Fvital to protecting our neighbourhoods
OL,18,Fand preventing harm.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@fO]wD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1772637084
OL,3,CHundreds of officers take to city
OL,4,Cstreets as part of force crackdown on
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"I want to thank Merseyside Police and
OL,8,Fall our partners for their hard work
OL,9,Fand dedication in delivering this
OL,10,Foperation.
OL,12,F"To those involved in criminality,
OL,13,Ftoday's activity demonstrates that
OL,14,Fthere is no hiding place. The safety
OL,15,Fand wellbeing of our communities will
OL,16,Falways come first."
OL,18,FIn December 2025, a similar operation
OL,19,Fwas carried out in Stockbridge Village
OL,20,Fand Huyton and led to 49 arrests.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@SO]
